      "title": "Traffic in Nugegoda due to NPP protest march",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Stanley Tilakaratne Mawatha in Nugegoda is blocked from High Level Road to Pagoda Junction due to a protest march.",
        "According to Ada Derana correspondent, the demonstration is organized by the National People\u2019s Power (NPP) led by its leader MP Anura Kumara Dissanayake.",
        "The protest march kicked off near the University of Sri Jayewardenepura and proceeded towards Nugegoda.",
        "It is reported that vehicular movement on the road is disrupted by the rally."
      ],
